I would like to request support for this Tuya Zigbee water valve actuator:

ModelId: TS0001

ManufacturerName: _TZ3000_wpueorev

Type: Water valve actuator (1‑gang relay)

Added as: Unknown Zigbee Device in Homey Pro 2023

Below is the full Zigbee interview.

Important notes about this device:
This device is a mains‑powered (230V) water valve actuator.
It correctly reports itself as a router, not a sleepy device.

It exposes:

One functional On/Off relay (cluster 6)

Tuya private clusters 57344 / 57345

Endpoint 242 (Green Power proxy), typical for mains‑powered Tuya devices

The device works correctly as a relay, but Homey does not recognize it as a valve actuator and adds it as an unknown device.

